"Demux" (Demux)

1. HLR_5: Multi-Variable Inner Loop Control (HLR#9)

Link to Requirements Toolbox
Document: HighLevelReqs.slreqx
Location/Item: HLR_5

Multi-Variable Inner Loop Control

The flight control computer software shall provide an inner control loop for pitch, roll, and yaw rate with low-pass filters that cutoff at 40 radians/second. The inner loop receives pitch, roll, and yaw rate corrections from an outer loop, and pitch, roll, yaw rate, pitch rate, and roll rate feedbacks from the processed AHRS data.

The following (5x3) gain shall be used to convert the (5x1) AHRS data to the (3x1) static output feedback:

2.211000

-0.310000

-0.003360

0.785400

-0.015180

-0.192300

-1.291000

0.018200

-0.085020

-0.119500

-0.019360

-0.012050

-1.895000

-0.004121

0.067970

 

The output limit shall be +/- 0.1 meter due to mechanical limits of the hydraulic actuators. The inner loop control shall operate at a rate of 10 milliseconds.

"PitchFilter" (SubSystem)
